 1993-11851993-06-030,  ,  ,  HON. ANDRE, 
PrecisApprove the re-appointment by the Honourable Harvie Andre of Kay M. LeMessurier, of St. John's, Newfoundland, as a director of the Board of Directors of the Canada Post Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, effective July 5, 1993.
